Source this path in the terminal before run the simulations
source /usr/share/gazebo/setup.sh

set the marker visualizer for visual data 
ros2 run yolo_recognition visualizer --ros-args -p subscriber_topic:=/visual_dynamic_obs_array -p publisher_topic:=/visual_data_markers -p marker_color:=green


Go through the following steps to run the simulation

install gazebo sfm plugin dependencies : for more info visit
https://github.com/robotics-upo/gazebo_sfm_plugin 

-- Note --
change the model path in 

   - gazebo_gpu.launch.py
   - all the world files 
   
                        as needed







